Disney has released a new musical clip from &#8220;Beauty and the Beast,&#8221; featuring one of the songs from the original animated film.Entitled &#8220;Belle,&#8221; the clip gives another look at Emma Watson as the film&#8217;s heroine as she sings her way through her quaint French village.The live-action version of the classic Disney film also stars Dan Stevens as the Beast, Luke Evans as Gaston, Kevin Kline as Maurice, and Josh Gad as Lefou, with Ewan McGregor, Stanley Tucci, Ian McKellen, and Emma Thompson also featuring as members of the Beast&#8217;s enchanted staff.&#8220;Beauty and the Beast&#8221; will hit cinemas March 17.